  "description": "A majestic view of a valley surrounded by towering granite cliffs and lush green forests. The cliffs are steep and rugged, with visible striations and patches of vegetation clinging to their sides. A slender waterfall cascades down one of the cliffs in the distance. The valley floor is covered in a vibrant green meadow, dotted with tall coniferous trees. The sky is overcast with gray clouds, creating a dramatic and atmospheric scene. The scene evokes a sense of scale and the power of nature.",
